    • Method Detail

      • book

        public void book(java.lang.String room_type)
        This function takes the type of the room as a parameter.Then then sends this parameter as a parameter to function searchRoom. The search function returns the number of rows in the csv file of this room if there is a room in the hotel which type is equals to this parameter type.

        Then this method creates a new room object- which holds room availability as not available- and sends it to the changeList method to print the new record in to the csv file.

        Specified by:
        book in interface User
        Parameters:
        room_type - The type of the room.

      • cancel

        public void cancel(int room_no)
        When a guest or receiver object invokes this function,firstly sends the informations about the guest which object`s member variables holds, to the searcCheck function to checks whether there is record is related to the object. If records found, room object will be created -which holds room availability as not available- and new information updated to the csv file with changeList function.
        Specified by:
        cancel in interface User
